 stations, and prioritize members during extreme weather. Some parks even partner with local pools for combo packages.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Do Austin indoor parks offer tech-friendly amenities?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Many Austin indoor parks cater to remote workers with Wi-Fi, charging stations, quiet coworking zones, and flexible hourly passes. Some locations host tech meetups, startup events, or offer corporate membership tiers for local companies.\\\"}}]}\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"26:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"script\\\",null,{\\\"type\\\":\\\"application/ld+json\\\",\\\"suppressHydrationWarning\\\":true,\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"$2e\\\"}}]\\n27:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"script\\\",null,{\\\"type\\\":\\\"application/ld+json\\\",\\\"suppressHydrationWarning\\\":true,\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"{\\\\\\\"@context\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://schema.org\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"BreadcrumbList\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"itemListElement\\\\\\\":[{\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"ListItem\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"position\\\\\\\":1,\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Home\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"item\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\\\\\"},{\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"ListItem\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"position\\\\\\\":2,\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Dog Parks Directory\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"item\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\\\\\"},{\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"ListItem\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"position\\\\\\\":3,\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Austin\\\\\\\"}]}\\\"}}]\\n28:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L11\\\",null,{\\\"variant\\\":\\\"light\\\"}]\\n29:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2f\\\",null,{\\\"items\\\":[{\\\"id\\\":\\\"city-hero\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"City Overview\\\",\\\"level\\\":1},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"city-insights\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Quick Facts\\\",\\\"level\\\":1},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"city-comparison\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Top Comparisons\\\",\\\"level\\\":1},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"park-col